r et annet aspekt som aktualiserer denne historien, som ogs\u00e5 er fortalt med gleden over \u00e5 kunne \u00abrekonstruere\u00bb 1970-tallets San Francisco og hele milj\u00f8et med forbl\u00f8ffende effekt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|film"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|film|filmanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c8e0ce704234d3294949ddfc63b6b4b460c87116968ec593c8c1279f6f9ed93b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-05T23:57:21.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Intens thrillerspenning bygd opp ved \u00e5 blande fiksjon og fakta."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1202884.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Zodiac"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e424176cf789b845c8b2049420adb4a2a5a95da6.jpg?597b9e1e"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "En intens film om besettelsens  krefter -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "e424176cf789b845c8b2049420adb4a2a5a95da6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Movie"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Movie"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "filmanmeldelser", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["film", "intens film", "politi", "besettelsens krefter"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["jack the ripper", "the zodiac killer", "the san francisco chronicle"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "san francisco"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["robert downey", "robert graysmith", "james vanderbilt", "mark ruffalos", "paul avery", "jake gyllenhaal", "david fincher"]}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/film/filmanmeldelser", "kultur